  "detailed_description": "Prisoner 17 is a dynamic first-person action platformer (In Death Run mode). In which you have to play the role of a prisoner who got a chance at redemption. Pass all the tests and get the freedom you deserve. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nRun and overcome deadly traps, destroy killer drones, go through the mazes, use a jetpack to double jump on special levels, act decisively.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- More than 70 types of traps and their various combinations. <br />\r\n- Nice Sci-Fi soundtrack.<br />\r\n- 20 long levels with different traps. <br />\r\n- Traps of varying difficulty.<br />\r\n- Beautiful tropical environment.<br />\r\n- With each new level, the game becomes more difficult.  <br />\r\n- Set your own time records.",
  "about_the_game": "Prisoner 17 is a dynamic first-person action platformer (In Death Run mode). In which you have to play the role of a prisoner who got a chance at redemption. Pass all the tests and get the freedom you deserve. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nRun and overcome deadly traps, destroy killer drones, go through the mazes, use a jetpack to double jump on special levels, act decisively.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- More than 70 types of traps and their various combinations. <br />\r\n- Nice Sci-Fi soundtrack.<br />\r\n- 20 long levels with different traps. <br />\r\n- Traps of varying difficulty.<br />\r\n- Beautiful tropical environment.<br />\r\n- With each new level, the game becomes more difficult.  <br />\r\n- Set your own time records.",
